i had just gotten and had thought succured. THEN i found out the nearest
two are in kelethin, *shiver*, and in feerrot. So i traveled my but down to
feerrot and got it. Then gated home and had a friend make the switch. Why
neriak doesnt sell a kit is amazing, then again, why ANY city doest sell the
book and kit is amazing. Well my ranting and raving is done. Thanks though

Nef
